{"title":"Hello World","date":"2018-04-29T10:06:39.300Z","excerpt":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2>","slug":"hello-world","comments":true,"updated":"2018-05-26T12:04:50.698Z","content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">\"My New Post\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a href=\"#Run-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Run server\"></a>Run server</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Deployment</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"完整格式：\"><a href=\"#完整格式：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"完整格式：\"></a>完整格式：</h3><p><code>title: postName</code> #文章页面上的显示名称，一般是中文</p>\n<p><code>date: 2013-12-02 15:30:16</code> #文章生成时间，一般不改，当然也可以任意修改</p>\n<p><code>categories:</code> 默认分类 #分类</p>\n<p><code>tags: [tag1,tag2,tag3]</code> #文章标签，可空，多标签请用英文逗号隔开。<strong>注意</strong>:后面有个空格</p>\n<p><code>description:</code>附加一段文章摘要，字数最好在140字以内，会出现在meta的description里面</p>\n<p>以下是正文</p>\n<h3 id=\"hexo-new-page-‘postName’-和-hexo-new-‘postName’-的区别\"><a href=\"#hexo-new-page-‘postName’-和-hexo-new-‘postName’-的区别\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo new page ‘postName’ 和 hexo new ‘postName’ 的区别\"></a>hexo new page ‘postName’ 和 hexo new ‘postName’ 的区别</h3><p>hexo new page “my-second-blog”生成如下：<img src=\"file:///C:/Users/xinze/AppData/Local/Temp/enhtmlclip/20160823_184852_854_6502.png\" alt=\"img\"></p>\n<p>最终部署时生成： hexo\\public\\my-second-blog\\index.html ，但是它不会作为文章出现在博文目录。 </p>\n<h3 id=\"如何让博文列表不显示全部内容\"><a href=\"#如何让博文列表不显示全部内容\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"如何让博文列表不显示全部内容\"></a>如何让博文列表不显示全部内容</h3><p>默认情况下，生成的博文目录会显示全部的文章内容，在合适的位置加上 <!--more--> ，这个位置之后的内容就不会默认全部显示了。</p>\n<h3 id=\"常用hexo命令\"><a href=\"#常用hexo命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"常用hexo命令\"></a>常用hexo命令</h3><p><strong>常见命令</strong></p>\n<p><code>hexo new &quot;postName&quot;</code> #新建文章</p>\n<p><code>hexo new page &quot;pageName&quot;</code> #新建页面</p>\n<p><code>hexo generate</code> #生成静态页面至public目录</p>\n<p><code>hexo server</code> #开启预览访问端口（默认端口4000，’ctrl + c’关闭server）hexo deploy #部署到GitHub</p>\n<p><code>hexo help</code> # 查看帮助</p>\n<p><code>hexo version</code> #查看Hexo的版本</p>\n<p><strong>缩写：</strong></p>\n<p><code>hexo n</code> == <code>hexo new</code></p>\n<p><code>hexo g</code> == <code>hexo generate</code></p>\n<p><code>hexo s</code> == <code>hexo server</code></p>\n<p><code>hexo d</code> == <code>hexo deploy</code></p>\n<p><strong>组合命令：</strong></p>\n<p><strong>用“‘空格‘+‘-’”隔开</strong></p>\n<p><code>hexo s -g</code> #生成并本地预览</p>\n<p><code>hexo d -g</code> #生成并上传 </p>\n","prev":{"title":"my-first-blog","slug":"my-first-blog"},"link":"http://xasxcy.github.io/post/hello-world"}